title: PMS 2.0 598 - LIVE From Radio Row In LA, Austin Ekeler, Adrian Peterson, Justin Jefferson, Darius Leonard, LeGarrette Blount, Jay Glazer, Bruce Buffer, & AJ Hawk
description: On today's show, Pat, AJ Hawk, and the boys are LIVE from Radio Row in LA and have a PACKED show featuring Austin Ekeler, Adrian Peterson, LeGarrette Blount, Justin Jefferson, Darius Leonard, Jay Glazer, and Bruce Buffer. Make sure you subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow and listen every day on Mad Dog Radio, Sirius XM Channel 82. We appreciate you all for listening, come and laugh with us, cheers.
